        "mode": "tldr",
        "content": "As of the most recent run (20260417_233350), AMD had the highest raw momentum in the entire 19-stock watchlist \u2014 41.7% 21-day ROC \u2014 but was in extreme overbought territory with RSI 91 and a bearish hourly STC cross. The daily trend is intact and strong; the hourly frame is flashing pullback risk. System sized the position at 15 shares (small) despite a 70% confidence rating because the overbought extension was too severe to ignore.",
